# Documentation maintenance (mandatory)

Before completing ANY task in this repo, read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/DOCUMENTATION.md`.

## On every change, you MUST

1. Append a entry to `docs/CHANGELOG.md` under `[Unreleased]`
2. Update affected technical docs (see table in `docs/DOCUMENTATION.md`)
3. Update `AGENTS.md` if constants, ports, constraints, or status changed
4. Add `docs/DECISIONS.md` ADR if making a non-obvious architectural choice
5. Never skip docs because the change "seems small"

## Quick reference — what to update

| Change type | Minimum docs |
|-------------|--------------|
| Terraform module/env | CHANGELOG + ARCHITECTURE + module README |
| Docker/nginx/ports | CHANGELOG + SHARED_EC2 + AGENTS.md port map |
| Scripts | CHANGELOG + RUNBOOK |
| CI/CD | CHANGELOG + GITHUB_ACTIONS + AGENTS.md |
| AWS constants | CHANGELOG + AGENTS.md + ci.tfvars |

## Doc index

Start at `docs/INDEX.md` for the full map.

Do not mark a task complete until documentation is updated in the same commit.
